{"tid":281312,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南韓想同中國合辦世盃     FIFA主席：會同習近平傾","createTime":"2017-06-12T15:22:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-13T00:36:42.000Z","uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0a7d16b3ff7a172c1b66f2eb76141c86d77cc8ce","tid":281312,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T15:22:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170612/large/1497277330_db75.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170612%2Flarge%2F1497277330_db75.jpg&h=aa383d24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n國際足協主席恩芬天奴近日出訪亞洲，周一到青瓦台與南韓總統文在寅見面。文在寅表示，希望可以繼2002年後再舉辦世盃，期望中國、日本、北韓及南韓四國可以合辦2030年世盃決賽周。恩芬天奴表示，會考慮文在寅的提議，並會稍後將文在寅的建議告訴中國政府。恩芬天奴周三會在北京與國家主席習近平會面，相信兩人會談到中國主辦世盃的話題；一直有傳中國想主辦2030或2034年世盃。中國外交部發言人陸慷沒有回應習近平會否與恩芬天奴談論世盃主辦權，陸慷說：「很多中國人都希望中國主辦世盃，我們希望這一天盡快來臨。」"},{"pid":"f35fdca5dae2218298b051c23b70a1fa9de9cc2a","tid":281312,"uid":24074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T15:27:37.000Z","msg":"日本一個搞好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"628c62731225c51004ebf941bb91d1097722b9d2","tid":281312,"uid":49316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T15:30:28.000Z","msg":"呢條泡菜總統係唔係明朝人？<br />\n<br />\n下下追住支那含<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2fc7274e125e438eef4c608f3e805e8c6b0d428","tid":281312,"uid":43809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T15:30:35.000Z","msg":"自己搞孔子世界杯好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15bfd482af7c9be22e25394173302bd094901d93","tid":281312,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T15:32:17.000Z","msg":"韓國同中國 踢波??<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[url]<a href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-9uRfNeKqTSM/UmdC2EzgCLI/AAAAAAAATfE/94tskNM9QVA/s1600/KFS77.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"htt